com.pb.sawdust.util

Class Pool.PoolItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.util.Pool.PoolItem
  • Enclosing class:
    Pool<T>

    public final class Pool.PoolItem
extends java.lang.Object
    The PoolItem class is used to hold pool objects. It is through instances of this class that pool objects can be retrieved (via get()) and released (via finished() for use by others.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
